title: Camp WeWow Shark Week Day 3
description:
It's Shark Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're playing Sharks and Minnows!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/game-sharks-minnows for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share! Have you overcome a fear?! Call us at 1-888-7WOW-WOW to share how you learned to tackled one of your fears! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!

See Privacy Policy at https://art19.com/privacy and California Privacy Notice at https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info.
